      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It's in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell. I'm only letting it go because I need something bigger for the kids. First person to see it will definitely fall in love!",
