      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of the 996.2 era, featuring the iconic wide-body aesthetics and a robust 3.6L flat-six powerplant. Mechanically flawless, the engine benefits from a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent bore scope inspection confirming zero scoring. The VarioCam Plus system delivers linear torque across the rev range, coupled with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory-fresh damping characteristics, and the undercarriage shows no signs of oxidation or fluid seepage. With its original paint depth consistent across all panels and an interior free of bolster wear, this C4S is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
